---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionSuggestion from '../components/SectionSuggestion.astro';

const base = '/Jo-Ah-Kim-s-History-Trip';
---

<Layout title="History Themes" description="A thematic guide to the historical arc of the journey, from dynastic dynasties to colonial memory and reunification.">
  <main class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Historical Themes</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">A narrative arc through Vietnam’s millennia of heritage.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="themes-grid">
      <article class="theme-card card">
        <h2 class="theme-title">Imperial & Dynastic Vietnam</h2>
        <p class="theme-context">The journey begins in Hanoi at the <strong>Imperial Citadel of Thăng Long</strong>, the political heart of regional power for 13 centuries. From the Lý to the Trần dynasties, we explore the foundations of a centralized Vietnamese state and its scholarly traditions at the <strong>Temple of Literature</strong>.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="theme-card card">
        <h2 class="theme-title">Huế & the Nguyễn Court</h2>
        <p class="theme-context">Moving into the central highlands, the focus shifts to the <strong>Nguyễn Dynasty (1802–1945)</strong>. The <strong>Imperial City of Huế</strong> serves as the grand stage for this era of absolute monarchy, featuring sophisticated architectural harmony and the uniquely personalized imperial tombs of Tự Đức and Khải Định.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="theme-card card">
        <h2 class="theme-title">Maritime Trade & Hội An</h2>
        <p class="theme-context">In the 15th to 19th centuries, the central coast became a crossroads of civilization. <strong>Hội An Ancient Town</strong> remains the most well-preserved example of an international trading port, showcasing a blend of Vietnamese, Chinese, Japanese, and European influences.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="theme-card card">
        <h2 class="theme-title">Champa & Mỹ Sơn</h2>
        <p class="theme-context">The religious landscape of central Vietnam is deeply influenced by the <strong>Champa Kingdom</strong>. The Hindu temple ruins of <strong>Mỹ Sơn Sanctuary</strong>, along with the <strong>Museum of Cham Sculpture</strong>, connect us to the spiritual heart of this unique Austronesian culture.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="theme-card card">
        <h2 class="theme-title">Colonial & War Memory</h2>
        <p class="theme-context">The late 19th and 20th centuries brought French administration and subsequent struggle. From the <strong>Metropole Hanoi</strong> to the <strong>Independence Palace</strong> in Saigon, we witness the architecture of colonialism and the sites marking the end of the Vietnam War in 1975.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="theme-card card">
        <h2 class="theme-title">Reunification & Modernity</h2>
        <p class="theme-context">Concluding in Ho Chi Minh City, we reflect on the <strong>unification</strong> of a nation. The journey through the War Remnants Museum and the vibrant energy of Saigon today provides a complex, mature look at the country's path from a feudal past to a dynamic global future.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <SectionSuggestion section="history" title="History Theme Suggestions" />

    <section class="history-quote section">
      <blockquote class="accent-quote">
        “History is not just the past; it is the ground upon which we walk today.”
      </blockquote>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .themes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .theme-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .theme-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .theme-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .theme-context {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .history-quote {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .accent-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .accent-quote::before, .accent-quote::after {
    content: '"';
    color: var(--color-accent-soft);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .themes-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .accent-quote {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
